item.title: Can't run client please help
item.dc:creator: @nzxt nzxt
item.description:
@nzxt wrote:

It means it cant connect to it. Are you running on a VPS or your own PC?

CBA to wait for a reply but basically – check your firewall settings and unblock for inwards and outwards - ports 43594 and 43595 or whatever your servers port it.
